<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Attendance Session Started</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        .email-container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .header {
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        .body {
            padding: 20px;
            background: #f9f9f9;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #666;
        }

        .button {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            background: #4CAF50;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .details {
            margin: 20px 0;
        }

        .details li {
            margin: 10px 0;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">TRACE</div>
            <h1>Attendance Session Started</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="body">
            <p>Hello <%- lecturerName %>,</p>
            <p>A new attendance session has started for your class.</p>

            <div class="details">
                <ul>
                    <li><strong>Session ID:</strong> <%- session._id %></li>
                    <li><strong>Start Time:</strong> <%- format(session.startTime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm:ss') %></li>
                    <li><strong>Class:</strong> <%- className %></li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <p>You can monitor attendance in real-time through the dashboard.</p>

            <div class="verification-container">
                <a href="<%- dashboardUrl %>" class="button">View Dashboard</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>This is an automated message from TRACE.</p>
            <p>If you have any questions, please contact support.</p>
            <p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> TRACE. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>